So let’s join hands and 
SAVE SOIL. LET’S MAKE IT HAPPEN.

latestPosts.caption:
Always leaning onto him, and yet never letting me fall.. always holding my hand , and lets me pass through all the hurdles in my life.. Today whatever i am is all cause of him,. He loves getting clicked, loves to pose, loves to make content.. never knew he had that side in him,. maybe i got this from my parents😜… #Always a happy puppy, living life to the fullest… No regrets , no sadness.. He just flows… You hurt him, come back and hug him, and it’s all good.. He holds no grudges in life.. Sooo much to learn from him.. A simple, humble , and grounded man… Love you baba ❤️❤️ @dtapankanu
To Father’s raising Daughters 
To Father’s raised by Daughters… 
What a beautiful cycle of life ❤️❤️
.
